# Frontend Rule

## Routes
- `GET /` → `public/landing.html` (marketing)
- `GET /app` → `public/app.html` (dashboard)

## Constraints
- No build step, no external JS/CSS dependencies (ADR-006)
- Brand: cinematic dark, electric blue trust, emerald approvals
- Tagline: "Compliance at the speed of intelligence"

## Preserve in app.html (all 5 UX upgrades)
1. Toast notifications
2. Skeleton loaders
3. Case completion ceremony
4. Animated view transitions
5. Rich empty states

## On change
Run `docs/instructions/IS-005-frontend-change.md`
